OL,6,FA separate British Transport Police
OL,7,F(BTP) survey released last year
OL,8,Freported more than a third of all
OL,9,Fwomen travelling by rail would be
OL,10,Fassaulted during their commute.
OL,12,FBTP data also indicates that most
OL,13,Fassaults occur during the evening rush
OL,14,Fhour when trains are packed and busy.
