OL,3,CViolent crimes against women on
OL,4,CBritain's trains jump by more than 50%
OL,6,FOn trains, the rail industry and BTP
OL,7,Fare rolling out a new, ongoing anti-
OL,8,Fsexual harassment campaign.
OL,10,FIt aims to educate passengers on how
OL,11,Fto recognise situations of sexual
OL,12,Fharassment, how to intervene safely,
OL,13,Fand how to report perpetrators to keep
OL,14,Fall passengers safe from harassment
OL,15,Fwhile commuting to work, home, or
OL,16,Fwherever their destination may be.
